<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3148520" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="2"><ahelp hid=".">Select the fields by which to sort the report. Fields can be sorted by up to four levels, each either ascending or descending. Grouped fields can only be sorted within each group.</ahelp></paragraph>
